# Automation & gateway

- Prefer editing **templates** under `automations/templates/` then exporting to `automations/live/` via established ops flows.
- Gateway changes must preserve signed ingress (HMAC, nonce, tenant lineage) and GSM JIT secret retrieval.
- Use `ops/render-env-from-gsm.sh` for runtime env; never commit raw secrets.
